ago, so it's a bit old, but...

67
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,458
...far as I can tell,
it's basically

68
00:07:23,541 --> 00:07:25,000
the same kind of
thing as this one.

69
00:07:25,083 --> 00:07:27,750
Then shouldn't we be
looking at his descendants?

70
00:07:27,833 --> 00:07:29,541
The probability of
a power like this

71
