being inherited has
to be awfully high.

72
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:33,791
I don't think that's gonna
help us this time.

73
00:07:33,875 --> 00:07:36,666
You see, back then,
the hunting was different.

74
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:40,958
So, logically there
shouldn't be any descendants.

75
00:07:41,041 --> 00:07:43,541
