in a normal situation.

89
00:08:14,416 --> 00:08:16,500
But we're not looking
for a normal human,

90
00:08:16,583 --> 00:08:17,625
now, are we?

91
00:08:17,708 --> 00:08:18,750
[SAKAKI]
Uh.

92
00:08:33,208 --> 00:08:34,250
[DOJIMA grunts]

93
00:08:42,041 --> 00:08:44,500
[MICHAEL]
