108
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,625
And how did you know
what I was doing?

109
00:09:27,708 --> 00:09:30,333
It happens
when you grow older...

110
00:09:30,416 --> 00:09:34,083
You can see many things
you couldn't see before.

111
00:09:34,166 --> 00:09:36,416
It happens
when you grow older...

112
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:39,166
It's really quite astounding.

113
00:09:43,750 --> 00:09:45,125
