114
00:09:45,208 --> 00:09:47,625
Never mind. Not important.

115
00:09:47,708 --> 00:09:49,208
Let us leave it at that.

116
00:09:49,291 --> 00:09:51,291
You are not from
around here.

117
00:09:53,375 --> 00:09:54,916
You should bear that in mind;

118
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,500
in fact, you might consider
leaving this place.

119
00:09:57,583 --> 00:10:00,166
[ROBIN]
I won't be in any danger here.

120
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:03,000
[OLD WOMAN] True enough,
you should not be...

121
00:10:03,083 --> 00:10:06,250
