one from the other day.

138
00:11:49,791 --> 00:11:51,208
[NARUMI grunts]

139
00:12:40,583 --> 00:12:41,625
[NARUMI gasps]

140
00:12:45,875 --> 00:12:49,958
[MEN gasp, groan]

141
00:12:58,041 --> 00:13:00,375
[MEN rasping]

142
00:13:04,625 --> 00:13:05,666
[NARUMI gasps]

143
00:13:38,916 --> 00:13:41,333
That's the third one...

144
00:13:41,416 --> 00:13:43,291
At least this
was done during the day.

145
00:13:43,375 --> 00:13:45,708
With any luck, there'll be
witnesses this time.

146
00:13:45,791 --> 00:13:48,083
Well, I certainly hope
something like that turns up.

147
00:13:48,166 --> 00:13:50,041
If we don't get a break,
it's gonna be hard to keep

148
00:13:50,125 --> 00:13:51,166
the police out of it.

149
00:13:51,250 --> 00:13:52,291
[knocking]

150
00:13:54,541 --> 00:13:55,541
How did it go?

151
00:13:55,625 --> 00:13:57,041
It was a waste of time.

152
00:13:57,125 --> 00:13:58,958
Doesn't matter what I
ask 'em, I can't even get

153
00:13:59,041 --> 00:14:00,750
