155
00:14:02,333 --> 00:14:04,250
They're with the
Factory guys right now.

156
00:14:04,333 --> 00:14:05,916
Apparently, they had this
light bulb they wanted

157
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:06,916
to get checked out.

158
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,208
