159
00:14:08,291 --> 00:14:10,791
Something they found
at the last crime site.

160
00:14:19,166 --> 00:14:20,666
What's with him?

161
00:14:23,666 --> 00:14:25,291
[WORKER] What I want you
to notice is the pattern

162
00:14:25,375 --> 00:14:27,166
of the burn on top of the bulb.

163
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:29,416
It's also obvious to
see that it was just made.

164
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,916
Are you saying
is that it was burned off

165
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,166
by the witch's powers?

166
00:14:33,250 --> 00:14:34,958
Well, I wouldn't say directly,

167
00:14:35,041 --> 00:14:37,041
but I wouldn't be surprised
if the microwaves from

168
00:14:37,125 --> 00:14:38,375
the witch created a current

169
00:14:38,458 --> 00:14:40,458
that lit up the bulbs that
had already burnt out,

170
00:14:40,541 --> 00:14:42,666
and then they, in turn, charred
the whole area.

171
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:45,583
Should we think of it
as some kinda immense power?

172
00:14:45,666 --> 00:14:46,791
Yeah.

173
00:14:46,875 --> 00:14:48,416
[AMON] There's something
else to consider.

174
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:50,583
We can be pretty certain
that this witch isn't able

175
00:14:50,666 --> 00:14:54,458
to fully control his powers yet.
It's a lot of unfocussed energy.

176
00:14:56,416 --> 00:14:57,958
