177
00:14:58,041 --> 00:14:59,916
Otherwise, there's
no explanation for

178
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:02,916
all the damage to the
surrounding area.

179
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,000
[MICHAEL]
Is that you, Amon?

180
00:15:04,083 --> 00:15:06,958
Michael, what are you
doing right now?

181
00:15:07,041 --> 00:15:09,166
[MICHAEL] I'm checking the
background of the victims...

182
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:10,666
[AMON]
You can do that later.

183
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:12,958
There's something
I want you to do instead.

184
00:15:13,041 --> 00:15:14,416
[MICHAEL]
What's that?

185
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,333
