after him, so we
know why he did that.

192
00:15:56,708 --> 00:15:58,666
But the third one
was likely just someone

193
00:15:58,750 --> 00:15:59,958
who lived nearby.

194
00:16:00,041 --> 00:16:01,791
So in other words,
now that he's been cornered,

195
00:16:01,875 --> 00:16:04,166
he's beginning to take it out
on innocent bystanders.

196
00:16:04,250 --> 00:16:06,500
At the moment, he most
likely believes that everyone

197
00:16:06,583 --> 00:16:08,166
he sees is out to get him.

198
00:16:09,708 --> 00:16:10,875
[MICHAEL]
Got it!

199
00:16:10,958 --> 00:16:13,000
Here it is Amon;
somebody's crankin' out

200
