00:19:59,958 --> 00:20:03,666
Sakaki reporting in.
This hunt is now over.

255
00:20:10,416 --> 00:20:13,333
[MAN 11C whimpers]

256
00:20:47,291 --> 00:20:49,958
[ROBIN]
Oh... Amon?

257
00:20:50,041 --> 00:20:51,833
Are you here alone?

258
00:20:52,625 --> 00:20:53,791
Yeah...

259
00:20:53,875 --> 00:20:55,708
What're you doing here so late?

260
00:20:55,791 --> 00:20:58,916
[ROBIN] I was over at Harry's
place for a while, that's all...

261
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:01,125
--What about you?
--[AMON] Oh...

262
00:21:01,208 --> 00:21:02,958
I was just going over
the information that

263
00:21:03,041 --> 00:21:05,083
Michael found on
that witch earlier.

264
00:21:05,166 --> 00:21:06,583
The one from today?

265
00:21:06,666 --> 00:21:09,333
So what did you happen
to find out about him?

266
00:21:10,875 --> 00:21:14,458
Juzo Narumi, 33 years old...

267
00:21:14,541 --> 00:21:16,791
As it turns out,
he was a distant relative

268
00:21:16,875 --> 00:21:19,000
of the witch Michael mentioned.

269
00:21:19,083 --> 00:21:20,541
So you mean
that he was actually on

270
00:21:20,625 --> 00:21:21,958
the STN's list after all?

271
00:21:22,041 --> 00:21:23,875
[AMON]
That seems to be the case.

272
00:21:23,958 --> 00:21:25,458
[ROBIN]
Hmm...

273
00:21:25,541 --> 00:21:26,583
But it's strange.

274
00:21:26,666 --> 00:21:28,000
[AMON]
Hm?

275
00:21:28,083 --> 00:21:29,666
Well, you'd think that
someone with that much power

276
00:21:29,750 --> 00:21:32,208
would be a little closer to
the top of the suspect list.

277
00:21:32,291 --> 00:21:34,291
They said there
were basically no signs

278
00:21:34,375 --> 00:21:36,166
that Narumi had
powers up until now.

279
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:38,375
What do they mean
"basically no signs"?

280
00:21:38,458 --> 00:21:40,958
And if he had all that power,
how could he hide it?

281
00:21:41,041 --> 00:21:43,791
Do you suppose he was
just awakened to his craft?

282
00:21:43,875 --> 00:21:45,625
[gasps]

283
00:21:45,708 --> 00:21:47,500
Is something wrong?

284
00:21:47,583 --> 00:21:50,166
No, it's nothing...

285
00:22:16,083 --> 00:22:19,333
When all is finally
said and done...

286
00:22:19,416 --> 00:22:22,833
...the words of time proved
far too heavy a burden...

287
00:22:37,583 --> 00:22:39,458
However...

288
00:22:39,541 --> 00:22:41,583
You are...

289
00:24:17,916 --> 00:24:20,666
[NARRATOR] Three hundred
and twenty years have passed

290
00:24:20,750 --> 00:24:23,500
since the coven
sank in the dark.

291
00:24:23,583 --> 00:24:29,500
Enchanting voice, forgotten
past, time sunk in darkness...

292
00:24:29,583 --> 00:24:32,208
Deep down in murky water,

293
00:24:32,291 --> 00:24:36,333
I touch the soul that
has wandered in eternity.

